column25: Illumina TruSeq RNA Sample Prep Kit, mRNA
column27: Bases were called with the Illumina CASAVA 1.7 pipeline
column28: mRNA-Seq reads were aligned against UCSC hg19 genome build with tophat 2.0.1, parameters --read-mismatches=3 --read-edit-dist=3 --max-multihits=20 --splice-mismatches=1 --microexon-search --coverage-search --mate-inner-dist=50 --mate-std-dev=50 –num-threads=8
column29: Aligned reads were counted against the Gencode v17 gene annotation using htseq-count in the HTSeq package with –mode=intersection-nonempty
column30: Genes were filtered from further analysis that had more than half of both HD and Control samples with zero counts
column31: Outlier sample counts in individual genes were filtered
column32: Differential expression between HD and Control was assessed using DESeq2 v1.3.34
column34: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: processed files contain normalized counts for all samples and differential expression values from DESeq2, in tab delimited format
